Data Dictionary - FoodReach UK

Dataset: UK Food Bank Distribution Data
Source: FoodReach UK Operations System (Simulated)
Date Range: January 2021 - December 2024
Grain: Monthly aggregation by local authority
Total Records: 2,088

Fact Table: Fact_FoodBank
Description: Core distribution metrics at monthly × location grain
Field NameData TypeDescriptionExampleBusiness RulesDateDateFirst day of distribution month2024-01-01Always 1st of month; no future datesTotal_ParcelsIntegerTotal food parcels distributed in month850Sum of Children + Adult parcels; never nullChildren_ParcelsIntegerParcels specifically for children (<18)340Subset of Total_Parcels; 0 ≤ value ≤ TotalAdult_ParcelsIntegerParcels for adults510Subset of Total_Parcels; 0 ≤ value ≤ TotalPct_ChildrenPercentagePercentage of parcels for children40.0%Calculated: Children ÷ TotalDeprivation_DecileIntegerONS deprivation ranking of area21 = most deprived, 10 = least deprivedLocation_KeyIntegerForeign key to DimLocation15Links to unique location identifierReferral_KeyIntegerForeign key to DimReferral3Links to referral source

